ED_Title: Financing  of the United Nations Mission in East Timor
ED_DecisionText: At its 99th plenary meeting, on 1 September 2023, the General Assembly decided to defer consideration of the item entitled “Financing of the United Nations Mission in East Timor” and to include it in the draft agenda of its seventy-eighth session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of the text of this decision will be contained in document A/77/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
